==Definition==

<b>trapezoid</b> (<i>noun</i>), plural <b>trapezoids</b>
# (<i>mathematics</i>)
1. (in the US) A four-sided [[polygon]] with exactly two parallel sides (known as a [[trapezium]] in the UK)
2. (in the UK) A four-sided [[polygon]] with no two sides parallel (known as a [[trapezium]] in the US)

